data.description: Great opportunity for owner-occupant or Investor! 2 bed, 2.5 bath home on a corner lot in Callaway Corners subdivision. Newer interior paint, bamboo wood flooring throughout main level, stairs, and hallway, LVP in bedrooms. Granite counters in kitchen and bathrooms, stainless steel appliances, Hardie board siding, and a metal roof. Main level covered porch & upper-level balcony, privacy fenced backyard area. Pics are from when last vacant in Jan'23. **All sizes & measurements are approx, pls verify if important**
